          .col-md-4.col-sm-12
            h5 Solution
            p Clyn strives to become a reliable application among households to conveniently locate home services to help with their monthly and one-time needs.

            p Exquisite Software created a two-sided mobile application for Clyn, allowing Cleaners to sign up, and give their business mobile presence, earn rewards, and have the ability to receive reviews from their jobs within the platform. Add this paragraph when the application is complete.

            p Consumers have the ability to locate and find Cleaners that have been background checked, easily schedule appointments, and split payments between their households.

            p With Clyn successfully growing their platform in multiple countries throughout the world, it was essential that our implementations help Clyn with the foundation for their business, in return the prototype has received great feedback.

